@node about_me
@{b}About Me And The Game@{ub}

 My name is Chris Spicer. This game was written over a period of about a 
year, with huge gaps in between bouts of working on the project. My spare
time has been split between working on this, writing reviews for an Amiga
fanzine, writing and drawing comics, drinking, reading, and generally
messing around on my Amiga, an A1200 which I love dearly. Oh yeah, and
having major facial surgery.

 What next? Well, I already have ideas for the next Minnesota Smith game, so
hopefully I'll start work on that soon. Look out for it.

 If you want to write to me for any reason (as long as it's not to write 
abusive letters about how short the game is) send your letters to:

 CHRIS SPICER
